        "what": "A device-triggered ingest appliance with explicit hot-storage, cold-storage, and Home Assistant boundaries.",
        "why": "Long media work must survive unreliable devices and storage without becoming an opaque shell-script chain.",
        "responsibilities": [
          "bind optical-device readiness to one bounded systemd job",
          "preserve local work until cold storage is proven and writable",
          "publish operational state and bounded controls through MQTT"
        ],
